## Testing Setup

- **Tier 1 — Unit:** Pure-logic tests with all collaborators fakeable in-process.
- **Tier 2 — Integration:** Real stack, external boundaries faked.
- **Tier 3 — Manual-deferred:** Anything that requires non-automatable interaction; the tester agent names the manual procedure in its report.

See [`agents/tester.md`](agents/tester.md) for tier-picking rules and the spec ↔ test linking convention.
